<!-- MISSION -->
<section class="about-mission">
  <div class="section-inner about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="section-tag">MISSION</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Why We Built AnytimeHire</h2>
      <p>The traditional hiring funnel is broken. Recruiters spend 80% of their time on screening — reading the same CV formats, asking the same questions, making the same unconscious judgements. Great candidates get lost. Biased shortcuts get made.</p>
      <p>AnytimeHire was founded in 2023 to change that. We combine large language models, computer vision, and speech analysis to deliver an end-to-end recruiting engine that never sleeps — and never discriminates.</p>
      <p>Today, 500+ companies use AnytimeHire to run hundreds of thousands of interviews a month, saving an average of 120 recruiter-hours per role.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-visual">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="ac-row"><span class="ac-dot green"></span> Screening Pipeline Active</div>
        <div class="ac-stat">248 <small>interviews today</small></div>
        <div class="ac-bar"><div class="ac-fill" style="width:82%"></div></div>
        <div class="ac-label">82% completion rate</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

